

* CentOS 5.4 
--------------
	i386:
		rpm -Uvh http://download.fedora.redhat.com/pub/epel/5/i386/epel-release-5-3.noarch.rpm
		
	x86_64:
		rpm -Uvh http://download.fedora.redhat.com/pub/epel/5/x86_64/epel-release-5-3.noarch.rpm


* Install Git 
--------------
	yum install git


* django-debug-toolbar
------------------------
	download :
	git clone http://github.com/robhudson/django-debug-toolbar.git
	
	install :
	cd django-debug-toolbar
	python setup.py bdist
	sudo python setup.py install
	sudo rm -rf build/ dist django_debug_toolbar.egg-info/


* django-paypal
----------------
	cd into a2billing directory
	git clone git://github.com/johnboxall/django-paypal.git paypal


* django-rest-interface
---------------
        download :
        svn checkout http://django-rest-interface.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ django-rest-interface

        copy django_restapi folder to python direcotry (for example /usr/local/lib/python2.6/dist-packages/) 

